<h3> Free Software </h3>
<!WA11><a href="http://www.cs.jhu.edu/salzberg"> Steven Salzberg,</a> 
<!WA12><a href="http://www.cs.jhu.edu/kasif"> Simon Kasif </a> and I distribute
the <!WA13><a href="http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~murthy/announce.html"> OC1 </a> decision tree software system. OC1 
is free for any <strong> non-commercial </strong> use. <br> 
